        <h1>Arithmetic Expressions</h1>
        <p>The following expressions demonstrate how to perform arithmetic using Jakarta Expression Language.</p>
        10 - 4 = ${10 - 4}<br/>
        85 / 15 = ${85 / 15}<br/>
        847 divided by 6 = ${847 div 6}<br/>
